Usefull Sql query and function

SQL Function
------------

1. Length
   Ex. Length('nizam');    Output= 5

2. Trim
   Ex. Trim(' remove start space or tab and end space or tab. ')
   Output =remove start space or tab and endspace or tab.|

3. Concat
   Ex. Concat('nizam','badhara') O=nizambadhara

4. Upper
   Ex. Upper('nizam').    O=UPPER
   
5. Lower
   Ex. Lower('Nizam').    O=nizam
   
6. initcap
   Ex. initcap('hello nizam')   O=Hello Nizam
   
7. Abs
   Ex. Abs(-22) O=22 Ex2. Abs(22) O=22
   
8. round
   Ex. round(5.4)  O=5   Ex2. round(5.5)  O=6    Ex3. round(5.6)   O=6
   
9. current_date/sysdate
   Ex. select current_date from dual;   O=22-SEP-21
   
10. EXTRACT
    day : select EXTRACT (day from current_date) from dual;    O=22
    month : select EXTRACT (month from current_date) from dual;  O=9
    year : select EXTRACT (year from current_date) from dual;   O=2021



